          "activation_name": "Take to the Skies",
          "effect": "You trace the rune on the front of the breastplate, and the armor\u2019s ephemeral wings grow tangible, granting you a fly Speed of 25 feet or your land Speed, whichever is slower. This effect lasts for 5 minutes or until you Dismiss it. Once the effect ends, the wings disappear completely, reappearing in their ephemeral form 1 hour later.",
